In the fourth quarter of 2004, the German taxable goods amounting to €11,600 were delivered to the German taxpayer.
In the context of the intergovernmental exchange of information, the German tax officer asked to verify whether the above Czech tax authorities actually existed, since the alleged shareholder of the German tax holder had established a number of sham figures in Germany.
